oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Radio interview conducted by Paul Olejar with Senator Warren G. Magnuson and Michael W. Straus regarding the Columbia River Basin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: From the program script: 'Radio Interview featuring Senator Warren G. Magnuson of Washington and Commissioner of the Bureau of Reclamation Michael W. Straus on the subject "The Bureau of Reclamation's Comprehensive Play for the Development of Land and Water Resources of the Columbia River Basin, and The Effect of This Immediate and Long-range Development of The State of Washington."
